How to compile:

%========================================
This benchmark uses two independent instructions per thread.
Each instruction executes N/2 FMAs.
%========================================
Compute benchmark
	Single:
		make computeIlp TYPE=float
	Double:
		make computeIlp TYPE=double
%========================================


%========================================
N threads copies n pieces of data each in strides of N.
Each data is float4.
%========================================
Bandwidth benchmark
	make bandwidthIlp TYPE=float4
%========================================


%========================================
%========================================
Intensity benchmark
	Single:
		make intensityIlp TYPE=float4
	Double:
		make intensityDbl TYPE=double
%========================================
